Package ca.odell.glazedlists.gui

Interface Summary
AdvancedTableFormat<E> Allows the ability to specify column class information in addition to the standard TableFormat information.
CheckableTableFormat<E> Specifies how to check table elements.
TableFormat<E> Specifies how a set of records are rendered in a table.
WritableTableFormat<E> Specifies how to edit the elements of table.
 

Class Summary
AbstractTableComparatorChooser<E> A TableComparatorChooser is a tool that allows the user to sort a table widget by clicking on the table's headers.
